    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting when you choose this tradition at 3rd level, you can manipulate your enemy's ki when you harness your own.</p><p>Whenever you hit a creature with one of the attacks granted by your @Compendium[mka.classfeatures.5MwNlVZK7m6VolOH]{Flurry of Blows}, you can impose one of the following effects on that target:</p><ul><li>It must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or be knocked prone.</li><li>It must make a Strength saving throw. If it fails, you can push it up to 15 feet away from you.</li><li>It can't take reactions until the end of your next turn.</li></ul>",
